title: Atletico Mineiro 1-3 Botafogo: Santos secures history-making maiden Copa Libertadores title
description: Ten-man Botafogo made history as they won the Copa Libertadores for the first time with a 3-1 victory over Atletico Mineiro in Buenos Aires.
